{"tid":2008471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet瑟琪登上世界最美百大臉孔！「單眼皮+腹肌女神」Seulgi的16個最美穿搭","createTime":"2020-05-09T05:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T08:43:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d32fb3b3d880b1aa26687b971c3f4d390a72fd10","tid":2008471,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"人氣爆燈的韓國女團Red Velvet除了隊長Irene，曾經成為「世界最美百大臉孔」第23名的瑟琪（Seulgi）一樣氣勢如虹。和成員Wendy同樣1994出生的瑟琪被稱為SM娛樂「唯一單眼皮明星」，身高161cm卻擁有優雅的身材比例，尤其是她的招牌腹肌和素顏肌膚令人稱羨，出道前已經有不少知名度，更傳出過和EXO伯賢的過往戀愛關係。<br />\n<br />\n唱歌和跳舞實力兼備的瑟琪吸引了玟星、黃致列等歌手邀請合作，綽號「熊瑟琪」的她更擁有girl crush以外的可愛魅力，她的時尚打扮也成為不少年輕女生的指標，更成為鞋履品牌Converse的代言人，她在IG也示範了不少的休閒穿搭風格！"},{"pid":"217712466e3d2f26b0ca6640c9c47c6968000201","tid":2008471,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://api.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/fashion/celeb_style/red-velvet-seulgi-style-file/gettyimages-940670536/25462183-1-chi-HK/GettyImages-940670536_img_1040_780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Ffashion%2Fceleb_style%2Fred-velvet-seulgi-style-file%2Fgettyimages-940670536%2F25462183-1-chi-HK%2FGettyImages-940670536_img_1040_780.jpg&h=92346f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到北韓演出，Red Velvet少了「最高成員」Joy，在五缺一的情況下第二高的Seulgi馬上成為最突出的一員。大家都是穿短褲露出一截大腿，Seulgi就比隊長Irene更加搶眼﹣3cm的距離，看起來很遙遠啊！"},{"pid":"d881223633abe25ad3c7f3bee071c6be4550ccb7","tid":2008471,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"瑟琪私底下是呆萌少女<br />\n<img src=\"https://api.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/fashion/red-velvet-seulgi-style-file/node_1673503/25461427-1-chi-HK/Batch-Screen-Shot-2018-04-20-At-12-59-16-PM_img_1040_780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Ffashion%2Fred-velvet-seulgi-style-file%2Fnode_1673503%2F25461427-1-chi-HK%2FBatch-Screen-Shot-2018-04-20-At-12-59-16-PM_img_1040_780.jpg&h=45c84ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成立才四年就不停捧獎，人氣女團Red Velvet除了歌曲之外，五位「顏值女神」也是大眾的談論焦點，Irene的是仙氣美、Joy的是冰山美、Wendy的是沉穩美、Yeri的是無辜美，而眼珠在長長的單眼皮下溜來溜去的Seulgi，則是呆萌美。"},{"pid":"4e28a472791aeb39ec5e499ca0c5393e5ead5d98","tid":2008471,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://api.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/fashion/celeb_style/red-velvet-seulgi-style-file/batch-gettyimages-484325268/25461607-1-chi-HK/Batch-GettyImages-484325268_img_1040_780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Ffashion%2Fceleb_style%2Fred-velvet-seulgi-style-file%2Fbatch-gettyimages-484325268%2F25461607-1-chi-HK%2FBatch-GettyImages-484325268_img_1040_780.jpg&h=ff3e62f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在眾多韓國女團中，Seulgi是極少有擁有單眼皮鳳眼的偶像，笑起來眼睛瞇成一條線，紮起馬尾、穿起學院風連身裙時特別有清純少女感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://api.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/fashion/celeb_style/red-velvet-seulgi-style-file/batch-gettyimages-871218598/25461553-1-chi-HK/Batch-GettyImages-871218598_img_1040_780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Ffashion%2Fceleb_style%2Fred-velvet-seulgi-style-file%2Fbatch-gettyimages-871218598%2F25461553-1-chi-HK%2FBatch-GettyImages-871218598_img_1040_780.jpg&h=9a57b437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或許就是這種東方味道，加上天然呆眼神，配上一字瀏海長髮建構出叛逆與迷離的感覺，令到Seulgi打進「2017年世界最美百大臉孔」第23名，將位列55名的隊長Irene遠遠拋離。"},{"pid":"60363fc40d69cb426da38a3406e6afb284572be9","tid":2008471,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"舞台上是魅惑女神<br />\n<img src=\"https://api.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/fashion/red-velvet-seulgi-style-file/node_1673560/25462561-1-chi-HK/Batch-Screen-Shot-2018-04-20-At-4-32-46-PM_img_1040_780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Ffashion%2Fred-velvet-seulgi-style-file%2Fnode_1673560%2F25462561-1-chi-HK%2FBatch-Screen-Shot-2018-04-20-At-4-32-46-PM_img_1040_780.jpg&h=c71622e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而不少粉絲迷上Seulgi的是她的舞台魅力，有別於平時一臉天真爛漫的模樣，台上的Seulgi彷彿變了個人，眼神也變得銳利起來，散發致命魅力。<br />\n<br />\nPhoto: sensible_k<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://api.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/fashion/celeb_style/red-velvet-seulgi-style-file/ghgh/25465902-1-chi-HK/Ghgh_img_1040_780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Ffashion%2Fceleb_style%2Fred-velvet-seulgi-style-file%2Fghgh%2F25465902-1-chi-HK%2FGhgh_img_1040_780.jpg&h=6a3137af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n感受到Seulgi的反差魅力嗎？在舞台上表演時一身黑色裝扮，披上Balenciaga的圍巾，展現霸氣酷帥的一面；表演完，和粉絲們問候時馬上變回一名24歲的女孩，眯起笑眼，十分可愛。<br />\n<br />\nPhoto: Mnet M!Countdown; Rickkong_"},{"pid":"779b7d33b4a336d5c32c6ee385e7adb939fc7171","tid":2008471,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://api.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/fashion/celeb_style/red-velvet-seulgi-style-file/ddd/25465884-1-chi-HK/Ddd_img_1040_780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Ffashion%2Fceleb_style%2Fred-velvet-seulgi-style-file%2Fddd%2F25465884-1-chi-HK%2FDdd_img_1040_780.jpg&h=7587bc42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一身牛仔的露腰打扮配搭搶眼的Off-White腰帶，充滿街頭個性風格。<br />\n<br />\nPhoto: Inkigayo PD Note<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://api.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/fashion/celeb_style/red-velvet-seulgi-style-file/batch-screen-shot-2018-04-20-at-4-31-48-pm/25462543-1-chi-HK/Batch-Screen-Shot-2018-04-20-At-4-31-48-PM_img_1040_780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Ffashion%2Fceleb_style%2Fred-velvet-seulgi-style-file%2Fbatch-screen-shot-2018-04-20-at-4-31-48-pm%2F25462543-1-chi-HK%2FBatch-Screen-Shot-2018-04-20-At-4-31-48-PM_img_1040_780.jpg&h=cc49a22e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以珍珠點綴的毛呢連身褲裝顯得高貴又優雅，亦突顯出Seulgi的姣好身材。"},{"pid":"a71838f69547761f56c55a817650459c3ce9f18f","tid":2008471,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"真係勁靚又勁fit"},{"pid":"c2c28e6fc29dd91135bca6222daefd611ae6f0e8","tid":2008471,"uid":76098,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amzMDwx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamzMDwx.gif&h=cbe65f71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e8f6aa0905b0ff4875d4d73841905dea610a112","tid":2008471,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2c28e6fc29dd91135bca6222daefd611ae6f0e8","tid":2008471,"uid":76098,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amzMDwx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamzMDwx.gif&h=cbe65f71&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"QQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQQ"},{"pid":"4b57414a5fe5b03febd893444322059af6293054","tid":2008471,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"我心中唯一嘅女神"},{"pid":"f69f8c048e250310007a4c4ff93d316f5c6c34a7","tid":2008471,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"我表白牙熊..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60f0192a936debbbcb66b97375c3c8687bb4da5","tid":2008471,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f69f8c048e250310007a4c4ff93d316f5c6c34a7","tid":2008471,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"我表白牙熊..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:35